description: Umami Moto won Cleveland’s vote for the Best Food Truck and you’ll understand why when you taste their wonderfully tasty Thai & Vietnamese fusion cuisine. As the name suggests, you’re in for a world of savory flavor when you take a bite of any of their delicious Korean Burritos (including Korean beef with kimchi rice, carrot & daikon, and cilantro on a flour tortilla) Burgers (like their Thai Basil Turkey), and more. We also hear that their crunchy Sweet Potato Tater Tots (with creamy curry aioli) certainly hits the spot. Umami Moto is the way to go if you’re in the mood for some of the most marvelous food you can find in Ohio.
name: Umami Moto
